{
  "stem": "24171.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we had to go there somehow, but till the-- you know, till the-- in the daytime we could go with the-- with the yellow stars.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But we had shortcuts anyway to go through forest stuff to-- to the fields.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So the boys went, and everybody from every household was and two, three chickens and women start cooking.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And nobody ate, because there was no appetite to eat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we didn't know-- it was no refrigerators like to put it away, it came-- started to get warm.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The next day, again, you know, the third day it was thrown out and start anew, start baking cookies, like non-perishable, something hard stuff.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We start sewing knapsacks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We should have more on our backs, instead-- not instead of suitcases but besides suitcases.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And-- and it was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was an awful week.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was 26, I think.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would have been 20-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Something like that, yeah-- 25, 26.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that was going on a whole week like that, that preparation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we start doing through the night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a neighbor there right beside us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The sheriff lived across that-- that creek, but right over the fence, we had a neighbor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at night, we went and we took over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had a lot of sacks of rye and corn beddings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had a lot of materials for-- it's different kind of bedding, like big pillows and feathers, you know, with-- from the geese because we had our own geese.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And whatever we could, my brother when he came home from Prague, he had beautiful suits.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We gave the suits.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, when I came back, one suit she gave us back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We got-- Barry got married in it.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
